@gateway = http://localhost:8080
@productId = REPLACE_WITH_PRODUCT_ID

### 0. Gateway 是否有啟動
GET {{gateway}}/

### 1. 建立商品
POST {{gateway}}/catalog/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sku": "DEMO-CHAIR-001",
  "name": "學習小椅子",
  "price": 1280
}

### 2. 建立庫存
POST {{gateway}}/inventory/inventory
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": "{{productId}}",
  "sku": "DEMO-CHAIR-001",
  "quantityOnHand": 50
}

### 3. 建立訂單
POST {{gateway}}/ordering/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerEmail": "student@example.com",
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": "{{productId}}",
      "quantity": 2
    }
  ]
}

### 4. 查詢通知
GET {{gateway}}/notification/notifications
